00:22:23,633 --> 00:22:26,562
I'm afraid of worrying my parents,

294
00:22:27,023 --> 00:22:28,664
of not having another job lined up.

295
00:22:29,633 --> 00:22:31,133
There are many things to consider.

296
00:22:33,484 --> 00:22:34,602
I think in the back of my mind,

297
00:22:36,391 --> 00:22:38,414
I believe that if I quit,

298
00:22:38,813 --> 00:22:40,008
everything will be okay,

299
00:22:40,977 --> 00:22:41,945
I'll feel better.

300
00:22:46,602 --> 00:22:49,296
It's like having something to hold onto.

301
00:22:50,797 --> 00:22:52,273
That's why I want to keep it.

302
00:22:54,516 --> 00:22:55,789
If it's gone, I don't know

303
00:22:55,805 --> 00:22:57,039
what will happen to me.

304
00:23:00,680 --> 00:23:01,758
Stupid, right?

305
00:23:09,422 --> 00:23:10,641
I kinda get it.

306
00:23:15,930 --> 00:23:18,078
That's how it was for me with Hiro.

307
00:23:28,273 --> 00:23:28,898
What?

308
00:23:29,859 --> 00:23:31,375
I think that was kind of cute.

309
00:23:33,680 --> 00:23:34,398
Like...

310
00:23:46,031 --> 00:23:46,914
What are you...

311
00:24:00,711 --> 00:24:02,938
What are you doing?

312
00:24:03,648 --> 00:24:04,625
You seduced me.

313
00:24:05,656 --> 00:24:06,766
I did not.

314
00:24:06,836 --> 00:24:07,523
But

315
00:24:08,273 --> 00:24:09,477
you didn't resist, did you?

316
00:24:12,539 --> 00:24:14,391
Where do you get the confidence from?

317
00:24:24,633 --> 00:24:25,914
Hirokuni-san,

318
00:24:27,758 --> 00:24:29,195
have you found your answer yet?

319
00:24:30,844 --> 00:24:31,469
No,

320
00:24:32,430 --> 00:24:33,008
not yet.

321
00:24:34,211 --> 00:24:34,992
Sorry.

322
00:24:37,703 --> 00:24:38,492
I...

323
00:24:39,859 --> 00:24:41,570
might not be able to wait much longer.

324
00:24:44,836 --> 00:24:46,891
The old man is going to be discharged.

325
00:24:48,148 --> 00:24:49,835
We agreed it would be until then, right?

326
00:24:50,680 --> 00:24:52,109
That I'd stay at your place.

327
00:24:59,961 --> 00:25:00,297
(Next episode)

328
00:25:00,297 --> 00:25:01,500
What do you want me to do?

329
00:25:02,016 --> 00:25:03,141
Don't ask me.

330
00:25:03,898 --> 00:25:06,031
Next Sunday, I will move out.

331
00:25:07,133 --> 00:25:07,742
Hey.

332
00:25:08,492 --> 00:25:09,445
Hirokuni.

333
00:25:19,125 --> 00:25:21,227
I wanted to make you wait for a while.

334
00:25:22,609 --> 00:25:23,562
Being involved with

335
00:25:23,570 --> 00:25:24,429
other people is serious.

336
00:25:24,453 --> 00:25:26,429
It's all futile anyway.

337
00:25:26,461 --> 00:25:27,226
You said it yourself,

338
00:25:27,258 --> 00:25:28,336
the rest of my life,

339
00:25:28,430 --> 00:25:29,742
I'll hand it over to you!
